= bootstrap_search_form games_path do
  - with_options :autocomplete => 'off', :class => bootstrap_search_classes, :placeholder => 'All' do |input|
    = label_tag 'search[players', 'Players'
    = input.text_field_tag 'search[players]', search_param(:players)

    = label_tag 'search[factions]', 'Factions'
    = input.text_field_tag 'search[factions]', search_param(:factions)

    = label_tag 'search[leaders]', 'Leaders'
    = input.text_field_tag 'search[leaders]', search_param(:leaders)

    = label_tag 'search[maps]', 'Maps'
    = input.text_field_tag 'search[maps]', search_param(:maps)

  = submit_tag 'Reset', :class => bootstrap_reset_classes(true), :type => 'reset'
  = submit_tag 'Search', :class => bootstrap_submit_classes(true)

  %p.help-block
    %i.icon-warning-sign
    Fields are joined using AND and values using OR (as you can specify a comma-separated list of values for each field).
    = link_to 'Feed', game_feed_options
    for current criteria.
